00:16:52.540 --> 00:16:58.540
[Guest]: Right. Whereas we know that the reporting structure is just so difficult to navigate.

00:16:58.540 --> 00:17:08.540
[Guest]: So now let me talk about the incentives of the victim. Right. And this is where the patriarchy is so important to understand and study.

00:17:08.540 --> 00:17:14.540
[Guest]: We most police stations are populated mostly by men. Right.

00:17:14.540 --> 00:17:23.540
[Guest]: When you have to report a sexual assault, you're basically going to a man who may not be as sympathetic or may not understand your point of view. Right.

00:17:23.540 --> 00:17:31.540
[Guest]: Second, we don't have any special cells for victims of sexual assault or children or anything like that.

00:17:31.540 --> 00:17:40.540
[Guest]: So whether your window got broken or your car got stolen or you got raped, you're basically going to the same place and the same procedure of reporting,

00:17:40.540 --> 00:17:46.540
[Guest]: which seems quite bizarre because sexual assault is a deeply personal and traumatic event.

00:17:46.540 --> 00:17:59.540
[Guest]: Third, even though we have both laws and social norms about protecting the identity of the victim, that's usually only about your name in the newspaper. Right.

00:17:59.540 --> 00:18:09.540
[Guest]: Everyone else in your neighborhood, in your school, at your parents' workplace, your extended family, everyone knows that you were the victim of sexual assault.

00:18:09.540 --> 00:18:18.540
[Guest]: And in India, all the honor and the virtue of a family is in the woman and her virginity and her sexual purity,

00:18:18.540 --> 00:18:26.540
[Guest]: which means that even if you have done nothing wrong and you are the victim of sexual assault, you have immediately brought shame upon the family.

00:18:26.540 --> 00:18:39.540
[Guest]: So there's this additional cost imposed on the victim and the victim's family, in addition to the trauma of sexual assault, that if you speak about it, there is a lot of shame.

00:18:39.540 --> 00:18:45.540
[Guest]: You immediately see people distancing themselves socially from the victims and their families.

00:18:45.540 --> 00:18:48.540
[Guest]: There's the addition problem that no one will marry the girl later.

00:18:48.540 --> 00:19:00.540
