00:32:42.540 --> 00:32:52.540
[Guest]: So we are complicit in this behavior because we think that if we are stronger and just get through it, it will be okay, right?

00:32:52.540 --> 00:32:58.540
[Guest]: The onus is again on me. It's my job to toughen up. It is my job to rough it out.

00:32:58.540 --> 00:33:06.540
[Guest]: And the more often I have done it and not called out someone for their behavior, the more complicit I am in allowing this to happen, right?

00:33:06.540 --> 00:33:11.540
